# ChefAI — Culinary AI Agent

This project is a **culinary meal prep agent** (genre: cooking). When extending or modifying this codebase, stay within the culinary domain. Do not change the genre.

## Architecture

```
API Key Gate → Onboarding → Meal Plan (direct API) → Knowledge Base (RAG upload) → Chat Agent
```

Chat uses an agent loop in `src/agent/runAgent.js`. Meal plans use direct API (`src/api/claude.js`). Document ingestion uses the .NET RAG API (`backend/ChefAI.RagApi`).

## Tools (Culinary Genre)

| Tool | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `search_knowledge` | Vector search uploaded recipe docs (call FIRST) |
| `web_search` | Web search when knowledge base lacks answers |
| `web_fetch` | Fetch a specific recipe or food blog URL |

## RAG Backend

- .NET 10 API on `http://127.0.0.1:5280`
- PostgreSQL + pgvector database `chefai_rag`
- OpenRouter `openai/text-embedding-3-large` (1536 dims) — **server-side only**
- Secrets via User Secrets or env vars — **never in git or React state**

## Adding a New Tool

1. Create `src/agent/tools/yourTool.js` with `definition` and `execute`
2. Register in `src/agent/tools/index.js`
3. Document in `src/agent/agentPrompt.js`

## Conventions

- Anthropic key: React state only, browser → Anthropic
- OpenRouter + Postgres passwords: backend User Secrets / env only
- Max 10 agent loop iterations
- Model: `claude-sonnet-4-6`
